President Cyril Ramaphosa will virtually address the launch of the 'Recover Better Together’ post-COVID-19 Campaign. * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa will virtually address the launch of the 'Recover Better Together’ post-COVID-19 campaign. The initiative is organised by Global Citizen in partnership with the European Commission and the World Health Organisation (WHO). The campaign seeks to create momentum for global COVID-19 pandemic recovery and a return to the implementation of global goals.